GRANDAPA BEE: I feel ya, kid.. I fought in the war of InBEEpendance, but we dont have time to chat. These bees are on the way to the last hive.

Military bee: say no more. I'll tag along if it means so get to blow one of those waps heads off.

GRANDAPA BEE: LET'S keep the PG rating..

