BOUGIE BEE: WHY HELLO THERE! You must be the brave bees that said our hive!

Cyber: Beep boop beep bop beeeeeep!

BOUGIE BEE: Yes, yes, well, I can't say thank you enough. You all should stay with us. Together, we can rebuild our hive with the honey you collected.
